  "description": "../description.md",
  "install_text": "Ensure precise livestock monitoring with the Lansitec Livestock Tracking Tag—designed specifically for long-term, rugged outdoor use. Engineered in a robust, animal-friendly enclosure, this Bluetooth tag continuously advertises iBeacon packets and supports up to six broadcast frames for versatile tracking needs. Powered by a rechargeable 150mAh Li-ion battery, the tag delivers months of operation on a single charge, even under demanding farm conditions. Its integrated 3D accelerometer enables real-time motion sensing, allowing farmers to monitor grazing patterns, rest cycles, and abnormal movements.",
